<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<?import javafx.geometry.Insets?>
<?import javafx.scene.control.Hyperlink?>
<?import javafx.scene.control.Label?>
<?import javafx.scene.layout.HBox?>
<?import javafx.scene.layout.VBox?>
<?import javafx.scene.text.Font?>

<VBox xmlns="http://javafx.com/javafx/16" xmlns:fx="http://javafx.com/fxml/1">
   <children>
      <HBox fx:id="welcomeHBox" alignment="CENTER">
         <children>
            <Label text="Welcome to the Equitable Resilience Builder">
               <font>
                  <Font name="System Bold" size="30.0" />
               </font>
            </Label>
         </children>
         <padding>
            <Insets bottom="10.0" left="10.0" right="10.0" top="10.0" />
         </padding>
      </HBox>
      <HBox alignment="CENTER">
         <children>
            <Label text="The ERB toolkit guides you through a collaborative process to strengthen your community's" wrapText="true">
               <font>
                  <Font size="15.0" />
               </font>
            </Label>
            <Hyperlink onAction="#equitableResilienceHyperlinkClicked" text="equitable resilience">
               <font>
                  <Font size="15.0" />
               </font>
            </Hyperlink>
            <Label text="to disasters and climate change">
               <font>
                  <Font size="15.0" />
               </font>
            </Label>
         </children>
      </HBox>
      <HBox>
         <children>
            <Label text="Equity and Resilience">
               <font>
                  <Font size="20.0" />
               </font>
            </Label>
         </children>
         <padding>
            <Insets bottom="3.0" left="3.0" right="3.0" top="3.0" />
         </padding>
      </HBox>
      <VBox spacing="5.0">
         <children>
            <HBox alignment="CENTER_LEFT" spacing="2.0">
               <children>
                  <Label text="What is equitable resilience?">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="System Bold" size="15.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <HBox alignment="CENTER_LEFT">
                     <children>
                        <Label text="Check out a definition">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Label>
                        <Hyperlink onAction="#glossaryHyperlinkClicked" text="here.">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Hyperlink>
                        <Label text="ERB centers equity in the content of the toolkit and the process for using it.">
                           <font>
                              <Font size="15.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Label>
                     </children>
                  </HBox>
               </children>
            </HBox>
            <VBox spacing="5.0">
               <children>
                  <Label text="Why does ERB content center equity and resilience?">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="System Bold" size="15.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="- Disasters and climate change tend to hit certain populations and neighborhoods harder than others, for reasons that often trace back to underlying social and environmental inequalities." wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="- Getting hit harder means that they suffer cascasing consequences (e.g., health and well-being, economic) and struggle more to recover." wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="- Resilience-building actions that also address equity are more likely to benefit those who need it most and have fewer negative outcomes for those already made vulnerable to disasters and climate change." wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
               </children>
            </VBox>
            <VBox spacing="5.0">
               <children>
                  <Label text="How does the ERB process center equity?">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="System Bold" size="15.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="An equitable resilience process is inclusive and supports community empowerment. ERB guides you through how to:" wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="- Establish a core team that is representative of local constituencies." wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="- Figure out who's working on resilience-related topics and expand your existing network." wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="- Hold community workshops to examine hazards, vulnerability, and resilience" wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="- Use storytelling to ensure local voices are heard." wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="- Collaboratively prioritize resilience and equity building actions that different groups will work on." wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="14.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
               </children>
            </VBox>
         </children>
      </VBox>
   </children>
   <padding>
      <Insets bottom="3.0" left="3.0" right="3.0" top="3.0" />
   </padding>
</VBox>
